data.description: MOVE IN READY 3 BEDROOM 2 BATH home in the beautiful Lake Mariana Reserve, a gated, lakefront community in Auburndale. Just minutes from I-4 and Downtown Auburndale. The kitchen features a large island, deep dark wood cabinets finished with crown molding and modern hardware. The master suite features a walk-in shower, garden tub, dual vanities, and walk-in closet. Let your senses come alive with the natural beauty and room to play in the fenced backyard, complemented with a paved patio and above ground pool. Mariana Reserve community offers a boat dock, picnic area, basketball court and a playground. A little something for everyone!
